{"tid":2432245,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大埔三名區議員被控參與非法集結 7月將由蘇文隆審訊","createTime":"2021-03-04T07:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T11:42:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"757e670f70dbbe4b8ec193b58951d3c0f70efccb","tid":2432245,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14138\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14138&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyvxF66oQwccw1TbdUPfwT%2FAY%3D&h=d43935dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14138</a><br />\n<br />\n#粉嶺裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#蘇文隆主任裁判官<br />\n#20200308大埔  #答辯<br />\n<br />\nD1 連桷璋, D2 姚鈞豪, D3 蘇<br />\nD4 文念志, D5 蔡<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n1 - 參與非法集結：所有被告被控於2020年3月8日，在大埔大埔超級城B, C區一帶，參與非法集結<br />\n2～4 - 無牌管有無線電通訊器具：D2～D4被控於同地管有無線通訊的器具，即一部對講機<br />\n<br />\n蘇 #答辯 (#20200308大埔 襲警)<br />\n文 #答辯 (#20200308大埔 襲警)<br />\n<br />\n開庭前控辯雙方傾在4月12日PTR，但書記忽然從後庭走出嚟，阿sir話今日PTR，律師們即刻同各被告密斟。<br />\n<br />\n12:15開庭<br />\n控方宣讀控罪(連同襲警傳票)，各被告<br />\n❌不認罪❌<br />\n<br />\n裁判官詢問雙方的證據和爭議<br />\n<br />\n控方有三段影片，共25分鐘，會傳召兩名警員作供。<br />\n<br />\n辯方對片段中影到各被告無爭議，會爭議當日情況的性質，各被告的行為，辯方舉例，事情就如街上撞車，有人圍觀。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官將三宗案件合併處理，控辯雙方不反對；案件押後至2021年7月26-29日，在粉嶺裁判法院第二庭，由 #蘇文隆主任裁判官 審訊，各被告以現有條件保釋。<br />\n<br />\n+++++++++++++++++++<br />\n(直播員按：11:15去到，一個人都無，11:30見到由沙田過來的旁聽師，去到11:58旁聽席上終於有十多人；案件雖然相對輕微，手足都須要支持呀！)"},{"pid":"dc94f405f05746f5afd7d8045a234d0a929752c7","tid":2432245,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:30:35.000Z","msg":"三名大埔區議員文念志、姚鈞豪與連桷璋，去年3月8日晚上在大埔區內一個悼念科大生周梓樂逝世四個月的活動中，以議員身份進行監察，卻被指涉嫌參與非法集結，警方落案起訴包括他們在內的五名被捕男子。五人今天在粉嶺裁判法院否認控罪，案件訂於7月26日審訊，被告獲准繼續保釋候審。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指五人於去年3月8日在大埔安邦路近大埔超級城B區及C區一帶，與其他不知名人士參與非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/FJYSZPBK2BFANMT2BXYXGTP5R4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2FFJYSZPBK2BFANMT2BXYXGTP5R4%2F&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyvxF66oQwccw1TbdUPfwT%2FAY%3D&h=20699f52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210304%2FFJYSZPBK2BFANMT2BXYXGTP5R4%2F&h=50fcf428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210304/FJYSZPBK2BFANMT2BXYXGTP5R4/</a>"},{"pid":"04beadf6f266ebb8cfe36968591c40c10a3fbe05","tid":2432245,"uid":53498,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:31:20.000Z","msg":"蘇狗係咪100%定罪？"},{"pid":"4717e4457e1436d17b849243b41b7520959c7055","tid":2432245,"uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:34:05.000Z","msg":"三名大埔區議員文念志、姚鈞豪與連桷璋，去年3月8日晚上在大埔區內一個悼念科大生周梓樂逝世四個月的活動中，<span class=\"xx-large\">以議員身份進行監察</span>，卻被指涉嫌參與非法集結<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌，人地話明監察都要屈鳩人非法集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地民選議員嚟嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3c0e733504607959ca977e9d2dae4a72bde615","tid":2432245,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31aaebbe65e405f513ea2c41c18d0dd0ea962651","tid":2432245,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"04beadf6f266ebb8cfe36968591c40c10a3fbe05","tid":2432245,"uid":53498,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:31:20.000Z","msg":"蘇狗係咪100%定罪？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:42:40.000Z","msg":"唔係 除咗莫 鄭 之外冇人100%"},{"pid":"c0a1e00e5e74e55ac3dbc7dc0a8a6375a2ac5acc","tid":2432245,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:10:4